did.abstract: Contains legislative files, subject files, and general files, which include a smattering of clippings, correspondence, and miscellaneous materials.

scopecontent.head: Collection Scope and Content Summary
scopecontent.p: Contains legislative files, subject files, and general files, which include a smattering of clippings, correspondence, and miscellaneous materials.

bioghist.head: Biography
bioghist.p: Art Torres was a California state senator for many years. After retiring from the Senate, he became the President of the Democratic Party of California.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Art Torres Papers. M0881. Dept. of Special Collections, Stanford University Libraries, Stanford, Calif.

userestrict.head: Publication Rights
userestrict.p: Property rights reside with the repository. Literary rights reside with the creators of the documents or their heirs. To obtain permission to publish or reproduce, please contact the Public Services Librarian of the Dept. of Special Collections.
